    Uy\ar [r, "h"]\ar [l, "t", bend left=50] &
    z\ar [l, "s", bend left]
  \end {tikzcd}


 in C, i.e. in paricular x\overset {f,g}{\rightrightarrows } y is a parallel pair in D.

The underlying fork of any split coequalizer 




